structure.unit: TRAFFIC REGULATIONS -- VEHICLE EQUIPMENT AND STORAGE

law.history: Repealed 1950 Ky. Acts ch. 115, par. 1. -- Created 1946 Ky. Acts ch. 15, sec. 1.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Increase of height, weight and length limits for trucks and semitrailer trucks on certain designated highways; maximum limits.
